  "title": "Thousands of British Steel jobs at risk after owner rejects government offer to go green - NewsBreak",
  "text": "More than 2,000 jobs at British Steel could be at risk, after Chinese parent company Jingye rejected a £500m subsidy offer from the UK government - leading to talks over the possible closure of two furnaces. A public announcement is expected soon, said one trade union on Thursday morning, with more than half of British Steel’s workforce potentially impacted. More to follow...",
